{
  "info": {
    "name": "TikTok Shop API - Direct Testing (Live)",
    "description": "Direct testing of TikTok Shop Partner API with real credentials.\n\nREQUIRES: TikTok app approval + OAuth shop connection for most endpoints.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n1. Import this collection\n2. Variables are pre-filled with your credentials\n3. Signature generation handled by Pre-request Script\n4. Test public endpoints first (categories, brands)\n5. OAuth endpoints require shop connection",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "tiktok_base_url",
      "value": "https://open-api.tiktokglobalshop.com",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "app_key",
      "value": "6h57b6tdd0g9b",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "app_secret",
      "value": "bfe6a5a4fd975239e226179dc6d8bb5f7c124880",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Leave empty until OAuth shop connected"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_version",
      "value": "202309",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Auto-generate TikTok HMAC-SHA256 signature",
          "const CryptoJS = require('crypto-js');",
          "",
          "// Get variables",
          "const appSecret = pm.collectionVariables.get('app_secret');",
          "const appKey = pm.collectionVariables.get('app_key');",
          "const accessToken = pm.collectionVariables.get('access_token') || '';",
          "",
          "// Get path from request URL",
          "const url = pm.request.url.toString();",
          "const urlObj = new URL(url);",
          "const path = urlObj.pathname;",
          "",
          "// Generate timestamp",
          "const timestamp = Math.floor(Date.now() / 1000);",
          "",
          "// Get request body",
          "let body = '';",
          "if (pm.request.body && (pm.request.method === 'POST' || pm.request.method === 'PUT')) {",
          "    body = pm.request.body.raw || '';",
          "}",
          "",
          "// Build signature string",
          "let signString = appSecret + path + timestamp + appKey + accessToken;",
          "if (body) {",
          "    signString += body;",
          "}",
          "signString += appSecret;",
          "",
          "// Generate HMAC-SHA256 signature",
          "const signature = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(signString, appSecret).toString(CryptoJS.enc.Hex);",
          "",
          "// Set variables for use in request",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('timestamp', timestamp);",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('signature', signature);",
          "",
          "console.log('=== TikTok Signature Generated ===');",
          "console.log('Path:', path);",
          "console.log('Timestamp:', timestamp);",
          "console.log('Signature:', signature.substring(0, 32) + '...');",
          "console.log('Access Token:', accessToken ? 'Present' : 'Empty');",
          ""
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Public Endpoints (No OAuth Required)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Product Categories",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{tiktok_base_url}}/product/{{api_version}}/categories?app_key={{app_key}}&timestamp={{timestamp}}&version={{api_version}}&sign={{signature}}",
              "host": ["{{tiktok_base_url}}"],
              "path": ["product", "{{api_version}}", "categories"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "app_key", "value": "{{app_key}}"},
                {"key": "timestamp", "value": "{{timestamp}}"},
                {"key": "version", "value": "{{api_version}}"},
                {"key": "sign", "value": "{{signature}}"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Gets available product categories. May require access_token depending on TikTok's current API requirements."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Brand List",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{tiktok_base_url}}/product/{{api_version}}/brands?app_key={{app_key}}&timestamp={{timestamp}}&version={{api_version}}&sign={{signature}}",
              "host": ["{{tiktok_base_url}}"],
              "path": ["product", "{{api_version}}", "brands"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "app_key", "value": "{{app_key}}"},
                {"key": "timestamp", "value": "{{timestamp}}"},
                {"key": "version", "value": "{{api_version}}"},
                {"key": "sign", "value": "{{signature}}"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Gets available product brands. May require access_token depending on TikTok's current API requirements."
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoints that may work without OAuth shop connection (check TikTok's current requirements)"
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Shop Authorization (Requires OAuth)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Authorized Shops",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-tts-access-token",
                "value": "{{access_token}}",
                "description": "Required after OAuth connection"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{tiktok_base_url}}/authorization/{{api_version}}/shops?app_key={{app_key}}&timestamp={{timestamp}}&access_token={{access_token}}&version={{api_version}}&sign={{signature}}",
              "host": ["{{tiktok_base_url}}"],
              "path": ["authorization", "{{api_version}}", "shops"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "app_key", "value": "{{app_key}}"},
                {"key": "timestamp", "value": "{{timestamp}}"},
                {"key": "access_token", "value": "{{access_token}}"},
                {"key": "version", "value": "{{api_version}}"},
                {"key": "sign", "value": "{{signature}}"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Gets list of authorized shops. Requires OAuth connection first.\n\n**Steps to connect:**\n1. Complete OAuth flow via your staging app\n2. Copy access_token from database\n3. Set {{access_token}} collection variable\n4. Run this request"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Shop Info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-tts-access-token",
                "value": "{{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{tiktok_base_url}}/shop/{{api_version}}/shops?app_key={{app_key}}&timestamp={{timestamp}}&access_token={{access_token}}&version={{api_version}}&sign={{signature}}",
              "host": ["{{tiktok_base_url}}"],
              "path": ["shop", "{{api_version}}", "shops"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "app_key", "value": "{{app_key}}"},
                {"key": "timestamp", "value": "{{timestamp}}"},
                {"key": "access_token", "value": "{{access_token}}"},
                {"key": "version", "value": "{{api_version}}"},
                {"key": "sign", "value": "{{signature}}"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Gets shop information after OAuth connection"
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "**REQUIRES:** OAuth shop connection + access_token\n\nThese will fail until you:\n1. Get TikTok app approval\n2. Register OAuth callback\n3. Connect a shop\n4. Set {{access_token}} variable"
    },
    {
