          "path": ["get"]
        },
        "description": "# TikTok Shop API - Direct Testing Guide\n\n## ✅ What's Working Now\n\n1. **Your Credentials:**\n   - App Key: `6h57b6tdd0g9b`\n   - App Secret: Configured ✓\n   - TikTok API is responding ✓\n\n2. **Signature Generation:**\n   - Pre-request script auto-generates HMAC-SHA256\n   - Algorithm matches TikTok spec ✓\n\n3. **Request Structure:**\n   - Correct query parameters ✓\n   - Proper headers ✓\n\n## ⏳ What Needs TikTok Approval\n\n**Public Endpoints:** May work now (test them!)  \n- Get Categories  \n- Get Brands  \n\n**OAuth Endpoints:** Need app approval + shop connection  \n- All shop-specific endpoints  \n- Product management  \n- Order management  \n- Inventory updates  \n\n## 🚀 Testing Steps\n\n### Phase 1: Test Now (No OAuth)\n\n1. Run \"Get Product Categories\"  \n2. Run \"Get Brand List\"  \n3. Check responses - may work without OAuth\n\n### Phase 2: After TikTok Approval\n\n1. Register OAuth callback in TikTok Partner Center:  \n   `https://staging-api.brakebee.com/api/v2/catalog/tiktok/oauth/callback`\n\n2. Connect first shop:  \n   - Go to staging.brakebee.com  \n   - Use TikTok connector  \n   - Complete OAuth  \n\n3. Get access_token:  \n   ```sql\n   SELECT access_token FROM tiktok_user_shops \n   WHERE user_id = YOUR_USER_ID;\n   ```\n\n4. Set {{access_token}} in collection variables\n\n5. Test OAuth endpoints:\n   - Get Authorized Shops  \n   - Get Shop Info  \n   - List Products  \n\n## 📊 Expected Responses\n\n### Before OAuth:\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 36009004,\n  \"message\": \"Invalid credentials. The 'x-tts-access-token' header is invalid\"\n}\n```\n**This is NORMAL** - means your app_key is recognized!\n\n### After OAuth:\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 0,\n  \"message\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": { ... }\n}\n```\n\n## 🔧 Troubleshooting\n\n**Error 36009004:** Need OAuth token (expected)  \n**Error 10002:** Invalid app credentials  \n**Error 10004:** Rate limit exceeded  \n**Error 10005:** Service unavailable  \n\n## 📚 Resources\n\n- TikTok Partner Docs: https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2  \n- Your Implementation Docs: `/docs/TIKTOK_TESTING_RESULTS.md`  \n- API Service Code: `/api-service/src/services/tiktokService.js`\n\n## ✨ Notes\n\n- Signature auto-generated (check Console tab)  \n- Pre-request script handles all signing  \n- No manual signature calculation needed  \n- Collection ready for immediate testing"
      }
